{"tid":1738891,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔想場運動就咁完嘅同我入嚟","createTime":"2019-11-19T11:30:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T16:01:23.000Z","uid":198773,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"535e9a5a168114ede46e89ab773d93bc8eb6b9e0","tid":1738891,"uid":198773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T11:30:01.000Z","msg":"五個月，我地有幾千個手足俾狗捉咗，失明嘅，被自殺嘅，因姦成孕，強姦乜都齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係唔想再有手足受傷又或者被殺。理大件事都證明一被圍我地就收皮，白白送頭。<br />\n記住我地個目標係要攬炒，經濟攬炒，要班權貴感受我地嘅痛，所以集中火力攻佢春袋。以下地方都係狗唔會放tg嘅地方：<br />\n機場<br />\n山頂<br />\n高鐵站<br />\n豪宅區<br />\n<br />\n智取呀手足，唔好再送頭啦！救下你地推到所有手足都睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4791409e2a98f63df4b65b396449b47ac486f04e","tid":1738891,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:33:00.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"cc01c3a60a448ef41d9fc7ec34dea7287e6dad02","tid":1738891,"uid":17381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:33:26.000Z","msg":"智取 融入生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f4b2771dcb1a5e9b795ae10044fbfdd67f53563","tid":1738891,"uid":74672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:36:29.000Z","msg":"仲有冇啲乜港共建設project可以一齊去參觀下？"},{"pid":"c2a43c19e920524bac886bd006f75b5875a31745","tid":1738891,"uid":198773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f4b2771dcb1a5e9b795ae10044fbfdd67f53563","tid":1738891,"uid":74672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:36:29.000Z","msg":"仲有冇啲乜港共建設project可以一齊去參觀下？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T15:56:36.000Z","msg":"港豬澳<br />\n新田購物中心<br />\n河套<br />\n<br />\n有錢人地方<br />\n九龍塘豪宅區<br />\n大潭<br />\n九肚山"},{"pid":"f4f18f31fe76d93c4aab5c0a970cd09e03b1b80f","tid":1738891,"uid":266617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:01:23.000Z","msg":"各政府合署？<br />\n圍，開工，番去飲湯"}]}